  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Purpose of this study is to investigate whether intraoperative imaging using a 1.5T MRI in
      craniopharyngioma surgery is useful in order to increase the rate of complete tumor removal.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
